<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Actual it is not allowed to use such a phpdoc comment:</p>

<p>/**
 * @access public}}
 * @param  int $iTest
 * @param  int $iFoo
 * @return  bool
 */</p>

<p>(there are 2 whitespaces after @param and @return)</p>

<p>This is because there are following regexp:
/@return ([^\s]<em>)/
/@return [^\s]</em>\s+(.<em>?)(@|*\/)/s
/@param ([^ ]</em>) /
/@param [^\s]<em>\s+(\$[^ ]</em>)\s+(.*?)(@|*\/)/s</p>

<p>To solve this problem there must be a "+" after the whitespace:
/@return +([^\s]<em>)/
/@return +[^\s]</em>\s+(.<em>?)(@|*\/)/s
/@param +([^ ]</em>) /
/@param +[^\s]<em>\s+(\$[^ ]</em>)\s+(.*?)(@|*\/)/s</p>

    </div>
</div>

